"},"id":"b676d138-317d-475c-8195-3b1ef479b2db","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/f4dmyXrLP4ajXXwPz9Lko.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The MBP36 is equipped with a built-in thermometer, which is becoming a popular feature among video baby monitors. The temperature in a baby&#39;s room is easy to get wrong, so this is a nice bonus feature. There are also five lullabies programmed into this system to help your baby relax before bedtime, but there&#39;s no nightlight on this unit. That&#39;s not a huge missing feature, but it would go well with the lullabies in relaxing your baby.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56475-motorola-mbp14.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/f4dmyXrLP4ajXXwPz9Lko.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"f4dmyXrLP4ajXXwPz9Lko","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/f4dmyXrLP4ajXXwPz9Lko.jpg","alt":""},"id":"0d69ba35-6e51-4830-bb5a-8ee4b1594cee","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This baby video monitor has one of the longest-lasting batteries we&#39;ve seen. You can expect it to last for around eight hours with moderate use. When using VOX and other power-saving modes, you&#39;ll get even more than that. This is a great comfort, especially for first-time parents. Knowing that your monitoring device has enough juice to keep on going means that you have one less thing to worry about."]},"id":"c429aca6-67c8-4e36-b1aa-8dba71c7cb70","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"7b3b796d-2251-4944-b300-4f9331f7b92a","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Motorola has a number of customer service options to answer most of the questions that might crop up. There is a convenient general live chat option on its website. The toll-free phone number is specifically for video baby monitor customers. An online PDF manual contains 28 pages of useful information that could also answer many of your questions."]},"id":"7c9942a7-2285-4c87-97ad-6fd52a079040","type":